{"tid":1835271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今次武漢呢單嘢睇得出支那人係幾撚冇腦","createTime":"2020-01-22T19:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T22:44:52.000Z","uid":164479,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"abb47bbe14ad1f4e01e7b0ee6c198e2f371be197","tid":1835271,"uid":164479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rAsSoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rAsSoq.jpg&h=59c514fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到呢個報導就知道即使共狗同世衛有能力處理到呢個病毒，都唔會有能力醫得番呢班傻閪個腦，佢哋既諗法係信個政府搞得掂，所以自己乜都唔洗做，生活如常咁過。但政府叫佢哋唔好去其他地方但佢地又唔撚會聽，一係偷走一係就乜嘢預防措施都唔做。以為對政府既信任就可以防疫。與其話佢哋對政府十分信任，倒不如話佢哋其實係一班自私到仆街嘅野人。唔想付出任何野就諗住人地會幫佢地搞掂，仲要佢哋由細到大都冇接受過正常既教育，到而家仲有背脊向天既動物就可以食既概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />與其要更多醫護人員可能因為呢件事而冇命，倒不如一個核彈炸撚左武漢算數，因為問題嘅根源始終都係一班冇腦嘅傻閪。"},{"pid":"8c0d58f0d64295a29cec42b7177ec06e1db431f9","tid":1835271,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:57:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4069b9036fd2ef839912ca2866256f598a4c66b4","tid":1835271,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0d58f0d64295a29cec42b7177ec06e1db431f9","tid":1835271,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:57:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:59:26.000Z","msg":"年年有今日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8b2916a6851dfa8a2e5b3e4d9f2690d469d00b","tid":1835271,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4069b9036fd2ef839912ca2866256f598a4c66b4","tid":1835271,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot